DI1NzQx.KgnpV4d_kh0Xw69PrCiPeX0GulJ0282j0Ka_uYiculcg.NmFuRFYvA8dar2sGcVFw0b9dairvL9oG9N1ztc12Stcg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2268\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1706\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMjQ0/MDAxNjgxNzEyNDI1NzQx.KgnpV4d_kh0Xw69PrCiPeX0GulJ0282j0Ka_uYiculcg.NmFuRFYvA8dar2sGcVFw0b9dairvL9oG9N1ztc12Stcg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-283f220b-3cab-496f-bab7-9d83b30039d3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-792a51f0-00e8-404a-8b84-b58d67657c47\" style=\"\">XD 그리드 화면</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-81a601c7-997b-4e92-a069-b6fe631b7230\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-62fe4753-d0ed-4d82-a71f-77b5a739983e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-bcadfcca-251a-4833-a9f1-6904f5fbd036\" style=\"color:#555555;\">XD 프로그램에서 웹 1920을 선택하시고 [Ctrl + Shift + \"] 키를 누르시면 그리드가 보입니다. 실제로 웹이나 앱 디자인을 할 경우 이 그리드에 맞춰 작업을 하게 됩니다. 다만 반응형 웹인 경우 자우의 폭은 가변으로 동작하기 때문에 스크롤로 이어지는 세로 폭 말고 가로 폭은  1920 기본 사이즈에서 편집 여백을 감안한 공간을 띄고 보통 작업을 하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb8327e6-650a-48f0-8551-118a0bbe7b57\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-fceebb3e-7769-4538-96ac-d54737179ef8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a42e3fb-3ec6-40e4-ac4f-56631e0f4661\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6a42e3fb-3ec6-40e4-ac4f-56631e0f4661\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTU2/MDAxNjgxNzE4MDg0NDg2.iVCcKwMvSzO2HTp1E50Y0WniHHAQBWXV6LzaCEE4KfQg.DDBbg_1rARWIkuhyt6c-v4vVYx6eSZ-TzqvGS-ISMyAg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EC%9B%B9_1920_%E2%80%93_1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1920\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1586\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTU2/MDAxNjgxNzE4MDg0NDg2.iVCcKwMvSzO2HTp1E50Y0WniHHAQBWXV6LzaCEE4KfQg.DDBbg_1rARWIkuhyt6c-v4vVYx6eSZ-TzqvGS-ISMyAg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EC%9B%B9_1920_%E2%80%93_1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b27436dc-e21d-4ea4-b061-04d1bdfd3262\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-52b45583-e292-4738-98cb-5874745ac24e\" style=\"\">pexels 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-61ea1a16-f39b-41db-a12c-f4377fe2acd1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-550dec2e-4712-4061-86c0-19d2515b7a58\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e45871a0-9d59-4488-a646-20a651319f0b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">임시로 디자인한 작업물입니다. 이 디자인을 자세히 보면 실제 그리드에서 벗어난 것처럼 보이지만 그리드를 잘 지켜 작업했다는 것을 볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-64f0eb3c-5481-4fc0-8b18-f3cd6c318816\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-64f0eb3c-5481-4fc0-8b18-f3cd6c318816\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTQ0/MDAxNjgxNzE4MTE3OTU3._niLmlIUnJIkyxeZGZw8SA4dvkiKsRzAcT0CF6u7CL0g.5v9u0rb9_JuHV-pt6ImN-U1ddLpvTE9vf0SmTcen4Fkg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"951\", \"originalHeight\" : \"719\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTQ0/MDAxNjgxNzE4MTE3OTU3._niLmlIUnJIkyxeZGZw8SA4dvkiKsRzAcT0CF6u7CL0g.5v9u0rb9_JuHV-pt6ImN-U1ddLpvTE9vf0SmTcen4Fkg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-36db8fab-3b0b-44e3-b507-e4979c808f29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22077846-c5a9-447a-bdc1-74d595a6b3af\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1e7fc53b-fe66-4ffc-81c0-b28991bff504\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이처럼 그리드는 디자인 시 작업의 균형감을 주는 중요한 요소입니다. 위의 디자인은 10분 만에 샘플로 만든 거라서 좌우나 디테일은 완벽하지 않습니다. 그리드 설명을 위한 것이니 참고만 해주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c25a7720-e15c-41af-948b-ea4397b232f4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b94a93a9-7afc-4afb-be4d-27de631a8c58\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오늘은 웹디자인의 그리드 말고 실제 편집 디자인에서 통용되는 그리드 작업을 브로슈어나 카탈로그 예시를 통해 설명해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6db2c7be-93c0-4735-94ed-114630b8cd3c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-a3c4a67a-131d-4fb8-8880-d6690ece78e0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a523cda1-64a6-4729-9fb8-c6292cdc75f2\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMjI0/MDAxNjgxNzE4NDM2NzQw.uyXRxUWqN5xPebiGI8-uDn3l9D83z5fcmkO8JGDGHBYg.xHlpSaCGurzp7X8K0Y04TXA5uSw-06vbFKKQ1o5WsjUg.PNG.cookthedesign/Key_point.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"969\", \"originalHeight\" : \"238\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMjI0/MDAxNjgxNzE4NDM2NzQw.uyXRxUWqN5xPebiGI8-uDn3l9D83z5fcmkO8JGDGHBYg.xHlpSaCGurzp7X8K0Y04TXA5uSw-06vbFKKQ1o5WsjUg.PNG.cookthedesign/Key_point.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-230f7c2b-0e7b-4319-97ce-dbae71a8eaf1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5af3457d-f21f-47ed-b750-822238d6b194\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>편집 디자인도 그리드를 통한 레이아웃이 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5add3955-84e9-45b8-8cf0-e0476aced14f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-45a58e78-2a0a-4566-aabf-a607fc518dbd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">편집 디자인은 종이라는 영역이 가변이 아니라 확정으로 사이즈가 존재하기 때문에 그리드에 따른 여백은 더 중요할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-456a93fc-0798-448c-a81a-f7752c21b62a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b649a27f-532d-49a4-993a-6750ec11dbdd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b4b137a-7b88-48d8-a0ca-fbbae17f430e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea110b22-393b-463f-b227-9a593a05ea87\" style=\"color:#555555;\">절수에 따른 영역은 다음 글을 참고해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1b16497e-db86-4909-b3f0-991524fc39db\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e7be4b22-a0f1-4e81-bff9-23e533e4a9f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222895077740\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222895077740</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb51de3b-9c9b-403f-b595-bb75163eb9ac\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f1392261-a337-4c5b-9903-6209e1622a65\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45d0ca47-e431-4cee-9743-00dbe9859e36\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-20c3e101-a245-4a3d-9174-a3479f34e39d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">명함의 편집 사이즈가 궁금하시다면?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e2d9839-f493-4593-87d2-1a849f37921d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3f068a46-f030-40c7-8c5a-c0333165c88a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222999481109\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222999481109</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-74b3ceb6-7079-48b3-879e-2ab4ef61c52b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-262dd5fc-f9e0-4dad-8229-384109b7b96a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-946e54a7-7dad-4f3d-8c12-b6b05efa2a8f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223028083002\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223028083002</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3dc7ee4a-edb6-46b5-aab9-4794999fa449\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-671d7254-caf6-4cc6-9245-24ca801e16f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd6be093-9478-43ae-b0c3-9c60cab48c1c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f7988918-3d1e-4499-971f-52a443aff1fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">편집 사이즈는 재단이 되는 여백을 포함한 사이즈입니다. 만약에 여러분이 A4 사이즈로 작업을 하신다면 A4(210mm×297mm)에서 최소 2~3mm의 재단 여백을 포함한 사이즈로 그리드(grid)를 잡아야 합니다. 여기에 실제 디자인이 되는 디자인 사이즈를 잡아 편집을 하는 것이 중요합니다. 오늘은 A4 브로슈어를 예시로 설명드려 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b2f0352-4f52-4c21-9def-9fcbd399c575\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7b2f0352-4f52-4c21-9def-9fcbd399c575\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTg1/MDAxNjgxNzIwMTU2NTcz.WHbXLnTqhkFTkxfzlHBy9Y-hLhH2w9GLYNdqa-cL1LAg.jsQbiRZSJ0susixjVk5ChLwbwwrc2cKxPZ_JyoSvn0Eg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"967\", \"originalHeight\" : \"700\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTg1/MDAxNjgxNzIwMTU2NTcz.WHbXLnTqhkFTkxfzlHBy9Y-hLhH2w9GLYNdqa-cL1LAg.jsQbiRZSJ0susixjVk5ChLwbwwrc2cKxPZ_JyoSvn0Eg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-babb12c6-7a2d-407a-a207-9bc7099a868a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8f7c0c58-b787-4a8c-b891-904a8c8d53f8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c5d702d3-b1a5-4aa2-b380-e1995af586a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">코렐드로우 Guideline을 통한 편집과 재단 영역을 표시해 봤습니다. 실제로는 A3(420mm×297mm)보다 사방 3mm씩 넓은  A3(426mm×303mm)로 작업이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line3\" id=\"SE-e5938bc8-9b53-41c8-a84c-d4532ed04c9c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line3 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0304f5a5-39ba-495e-82e7-d03ded8098d2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0304f5a5-39ba-495e-82e7-d03ded8098d2\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfMTAy/MDAxNjgxNzc5MDA3MjYw.fzH5WNha0z6FEN6FNKtmjFOQGlM5fDDUWU9G8lg0lA4g.gqsX8Oi739P2QhgYn4afuscMxSGPdHmBRQ6a9n420X8g.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"5033\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3580\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfMTAy/MDAxNjgxNzc5MDA3MjYw.fzH5WNha0z6FEN6FNKtmjFOQGlM5fDDUWU9G8lg0lA4g.gqsX8Oi739P2QhgYn4afuscMxSGPdHmBRQ6a9n420X8g.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3b82dc7f-6d3a-4ced-80c2-f9ae818455c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2415d865-6d72-484f-acc1-32e6d1e7771b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c6de9f6-847d-48ba-9bca-2fe328ab5db7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리드에 맞춘 디자인 샘플이 있습니다. 여러분이 이 디자인을 보시면 어떤 생각이 드실까요? 일단 대충 디자인이 되어 있다고 생각하셨을 겁니다. 물론 하나의 샘플 디자인이므로 제가 총평을 하지는 않겠습니다. 하지만 위의 디자인에서는 몇 가지 문제점이 있습니다. 오로지 저의 관점에서 디자인을 수정해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c686ee1e-4cff-4bdf-a70d-fc2a0444104d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7ca5ae44-5a7b-4239-8e1b-9bb7748415e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-a10d511a-9d54-4f37-ac7c-eee31907a766\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-3b4027e1-e6a3-4668-b55c-991d815bbad0\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMjAy/MDAxNjgxNzIyMzE2NDM4.s6VqHJgcQRpb5i9LgUsg_UztHWJ1LMyriA9ZgKCYXMEg.PBvuufYP_tq0J1eE4eI_ft5fZCdIXhwK59JvL9RxYlsg.PNG.cookthedesign/Check.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"827\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMjAy/MDAxNjgxNzIyMzE2NDM4.s6VqHJgcQRpb5i9LgUsg_UztHWJ1LMyriA9ZgKCYXMEg.PBvuufYP_tq0J1eE4eI_ft5fZCdIXhwK59JvL9RxYlsg.PNG.cookthedesign/Check.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9e3f9e46-f1f3-4c47-abd1-bc3eb9530560\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b7e20602-d1ca-410c-a9f7-ff92455ba15e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>일단 내용에 맞는 눈에 띄는 이미지나 포인트 선택이 없습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7042409b-3fe4-43c6-af61-ca3a3133057c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-97297514-c99a-4590-b963-11fcfe2b929d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인에서 주목도는 가장 중요합니다. Winter Vacation Course라는 제목처럼 타이틀 글자나 이미지가 비슷한 느낌으로 배치되어 시선을 주목시켜주지 못합니다. 이런 이유로 이 디자인의 퀄리티를 떠나 읽는 사람으로 하여금 말하는 주제를 한눈에 파악하기 어려운 측면이 있습니다. 이럴 때 겨울 이미지나 그에 맞는 구성을 강조하여 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fb609356-acda-4391-8f38-44cc8a74be06\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\"><b>\"아~ 이 페이지의 내용은 대충 이런 느낌이겠구나!\"라고</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2b8a32b-5bf9-4c29-9f5f-ff376f517892\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 인식하게 만들어야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e5bc3f1-e669-48c4-ba7f-0db07786ae7a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7e5bc3f1-e669-48c4-ba7f-0db07786ae7a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfMTAw/MDAxNjgxNzgxMTIxMjM0.8QAVXbNZ5tcPNtaHw1vxWb0Tq6TGMoxnSSit6oE7aE0g.FxGgIRR09JGdcbqkcdcgrgGafCeLzI4EIazLd9mO2EMg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"5031\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2035\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfMTAw/MDAxNjgxNzgxMTIxMjM0.8QAVXbNZ5tcPNtaHw1vxWb0Tq6TGMoxnSSit6oE7aE0g.FxGgIRR09JGdcbqkcdcgrgGafCeLzI4EIazLd9mO2EMg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3bf9805-74df-42ec-b9e9-f844a3c91dfd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a11392d8-1c26-446e-8c87-5175ceb2af92\" style=\"\">pexels 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e6226f23-a4bb-4a01-b535-adeac94e09ed\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5f252ca-e487-44a4-87ae-23075be79fc2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7595f46-d38a-4f47-adc9-bad3281aa671\" style=\"color:#555555;\">상단에 겨울을 상징하는 눈산이미지를 삽입하여 겨울에 대한 이야기구나라는 것을 한눈에 알 수 있도록 집중도를 높였습니다. 이는 디자인에서 가장 중요한 요소입니다. 이런 주목도를 잡기 위해 고객과의 컨셉을 잘 잡도록 유도하는 것이 디자이너의 역할입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-903ec4df-d210-44df-85c2-ea7040b2f9c7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-903ec4df-d210-44df-85c2-ea7040b2f9c7\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfNDAg/MDAxNjgxNzgxNDc2MDE4.4Y3tH5ZOSTe8TXnVRIkuvgRSaxkiQK5zTDJ6QfiYWhIg.Mhc8hRV-HXtkYB3WOa0hVyWNw7jptm9jMUz0K-ga1k4g.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"778\", \"originalHeight\" : \"282\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfNDAg/MDAxNjgxNzgxNDc2MDE4.4Y3tH5ZOSTe8TXnVRIkuvgRSaxkiQK5zTDJ6QfiYWhIg.Mhc8hRV-HXtkYB3WOa0hVyWNw7jptm9jMUz0K-ga1k4g.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b7689c0-e28f-4d82-a0a9-931091b0181a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba393cfd-8401-4916-a258-b832350a961b\" style=\"\">pexels 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af6a07de-07fe-461f-a759-fe0fcf5c35e5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-297214dc-77be-4bac-ab87-1edf7f1a3eac\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-61deab1c-9938-4bde-bd59-d41bcedef975\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-3fc76d4f-2bef-477d-8ab0-32ea03ef601c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-52861759-92cf-4d46-9091-edf91951928d\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMjAy/MDAxNjgxNzIyMzE2NDM4.s6VqHJgcQRpb5i9LgUsg_UztHWJ1LMyriA9ZgKCYXMEg.PBvuufYP_tq0J1eE4eI_ft5fZCdIXhwK59JvL9RxYlsg.PNG.cookthedesign/Check.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"827\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMjAy/MDAxNjgxNzIyMzE2NDM4.s6VqHJgcQRpb5i9LgUsg_UztHWJ1LMyriA9ZgKCYXMEg.PBvuufYP_tq0J1eE4eI_ft5fZCdIXhwK59JvL9RxYlsg.PNG.cookthedesign/Check.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1cf2722b-18f8-41a5-9d19-9c5d6a6da64f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3c95595c-6dbd-461e-9efc-08c0a719a940\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>일단 여백미가 없이 답답해 보입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ec2f3cb3-cfca-4505-ab46-d839a39ee9d7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-a27ac3ac-69a8-4ce9-8d4b-72b992446eff\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\"><b>디자인 5가지 요소 중에 여백미</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4dbee311-fd17-4b50-bc20-557180bed9fc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가 있습니다. White Space라고도 하고 Proximity라고 거리감이라는 의미도 있습니다. 무엇이 어떻든 간에 디자인에서 여백은 가장 중요한 요소일 수 있습니다. 이런 차원에서 위 디자인은 여백미가 전혀 없이 그림과 이미지로 채워져 있습니다. 차라리 글씨를 줄이고 그 공간만큼이라도 여백을 살렸으면 하는 바람이 있습니다. 그런 측면에서 앞의 눈산이미지는 여백미를 잘 살린 디자인일 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6369503a-4239-422a-b73b-e8b7f257a79b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6369503a-4239-422a-b73b-e8b7f257a79b\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfMjMw/MDAxNjgxNzgxNTc0NTE3.S02hS2q9_fQK_bQnObDN6A_FasFuY4qMsThKbBiJ05og.g3GTWPIDqopR4TW8U6X-lvdjAu4Wljr1oLbYY8gJ_KQg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"5033\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3580\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfMjMw/MDAxNjgxNzgxNTc0NTE3.S02hS2q9_fQK_bQnObDN6A_FasFuY4qMsThKbBiJ05og.g3GTWPIDqopR4TW8U6X-lvdjAu4Wljr1oLbYY8gJ_KQg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0d55b64a-28ed-4ea0-a572-2cc4ea39d256\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7eaa21d-dadc-499e-8910-9bfd20b2cee4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7013851f-4a75-4ae2-894f-68eefc6e2b3b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">중간에 사진을 제외한 나머지를 배치해 봤습니다. 글자를 조금 줄이고 2단으로 편집하여 읽기 편하게 가독성을 높였습니다. 모든 책자는 첫 번째로 읽고 싶어져야 합니다. 그래야 고객으로부터 인정받는 디자인이라고 할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5b1fc4b-cbaa-4f88-b4b7-d04939a04016\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88b1d152-f17b-46fa-9c1d-3ccde4edaf3f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b38c7569-cfe8-448e-a369-d36af5ce3b88\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b38c7569-cfe8-448e-a369-d36af5ce3b88\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfNzAg/MDAxNjgxNzgyNDg3Nzc3.SVQYmF3NhVA5ZBT5P3QxTJG6waC7UJLo9GUw-P6W8twg.1U-kX2c0GDmpHZO0AVFvd4xkKO25FJYoaV6SL0CNivcg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"5033\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3580\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MThfNzAg/MDAxNjgxNzgyNDg3Nzc3.SVQYmF3NhVA5ZBT5P3QxTJG6waC7UJLo9GUw-P6W8twg.1U-kX2c0GDmpHZO0AVFvd4xkKO25FJYoaV6SL0CNivcg.PNG.cookthedesign/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-299d1c6f-c0fa-4341-a5a9-401ea36d5dce\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-78fd5c91-497f-496d-8a44-5d14f6a40fb2\" style=\"\">최종 디테일 수정 전</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-54e8955b-de02-4292-953f-7e9064abfbe4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2f44b6f-4cce-48bd-9f03-781a10efec40\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ad0d1f9-edb1-4dd6-ab75-4a80dc3a193f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사진과 서브 내용을 넣어 완성하였습니다. 사진 크기나 서브타이틀을 확정하고 마무리합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-967e1f3a-712b-46ac-b4cd-e587534433aa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-146abe3e-4bbf-46c7-9eb6-9d6332cc24e1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-76ea764c-9088-4e47-8466-521c13056418\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9fef8c44-2c6d-487e-9b40-97151835dbac\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>위의 디자인은 내용 문구도 틀리고 주제도 임의로 선정한 거이라 예시로만 제작되었습니다. 이런 그리드를 이용한 디자인할 때는 다음과 같이 균형과 통일감이 매우 중요합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9af8c5f2-feec-4a62-b620-ca21eab5efe6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a5ca6ad0-026f-4222-a758-da6fd3c57e68\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bdfe4a02-15f8-4033-8c74-e22cefc9e9b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a32f18e8-f8c6-454d-b33d-535ce911ed7d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">1. 양쪽의 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9a3478cb-a34d-41a8-84a8-2ca89b8f1c9b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">간격을 최대한 맞춰서</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e0959a81-5d09-4498-a478-e2ba81fd2c99\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 디자인합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7af567d5-7c18-435a-8f89-c14853961d7d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5419c0af-2e47-4627-9b63-8de84872a5c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2. 하단에 내용을 치우치도록 넣어서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c24db31a-1bf3-478e-a5f1-eebea27c85ae\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">안정감 있는 디자인을 선택</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b49c0234-aafb-4f45-b5bc-a42223266d60\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6cf1c8e7-b93a-4686-91e2-292107fd8446\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5039e117-a71b-42ae-854b-64bd4e6a6b1e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3. 제목과 좌위 상하의 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9cb961a-b626-4c97-b2e4-a104a78bceb6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">그리드를 활용한 맞춤</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-782d1a3e-e198-4522-8f07-e72c16f64fb1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 기본적으로 최대한 지킵니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-878e545f-01f2-4436-8253-5a1b4eae84a8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-80ed71f2-af02-4855-a20c-166831ecba66\" style=\"color:#555555;\">4. 서체와 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f6a3dcb9-2a3e-4bb6-aaac-bbb997a7f813\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">이미지의 강약</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c14b6632-8c0d-49f0-8e34-31f0ac46bf62\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 지켜서 긴장감을 만듭니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c5025fc-50b0-42a1-abc4-4b9f19290de2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1c88646d-0909-4dc7-8f12-bacde063fafd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-566b663a-afbc-4c30-b900-8be2e1dee387\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b13b27ca-a454-453e-baed-47a0eb930aed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-321b48e7-ff84-48ba-ad3e-69570a07361c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style